1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,560
Consort Lin, Her Majesty is merciful. She
grants you an intact corpse. Thank her.

2
00:00:06,160 --> 00:00:11,560
On my first day after transmigrating,
someone brought poisoned wine and ordered
me to die.

3
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:15,320
But the face in the bronze mirror... was
not mine.

4
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:25,000
Phoenix eyes, thin lips, a faint scar on
the left wrist. Memories rushed in. Her
name was Lin Wan'er, legitimate daughter
of a minister, a deposed concubine.

5
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:32,760
Three years ago, she was framed for
witchcraft and banished here. Three nights
ago, she died.

6
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:42,080
The original owner was already dead. Yet
the death edict still came as planned.
Meaning tonight was always meant to be her
death night.

7
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:52,520
Your Highness! Why are you up? Madam Liu
is here with the Empress's order!
Tonight... tonight they will send you to
your death!

8
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,680
Madam Liu arrives!

9
00:00:55,080 --> 00:01:02,880
Consort Lin has suffered here for three
years. It is time to rest. Silk, dagger,
or poisoned wine. Choose one yourself.

10
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:08,240
Please show mercy, Madam Liu! Her Highness
is weak. She cannot bear this!

11
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:14,240
Shut up! Drag her away.

12
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:23,360
Fight back? This body could barely stand.
Beg? Lin Wan'er begged for three years,
and only this wine came for her.

13
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:26,720
Do not be afraid, Your Highness. Drink it.
It will not hurt.

14
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:33,040
Bitter almond scent. Poisoned wine. They
would not even give me time to cry.

15
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:35,840
At a time like this... why are you
smiling?

16
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:40,800
I am smiling because you are impatient. So
impatient you would kill a dead woman
twice.

17
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,172
Host near death. Ten Thousand Demon
Bloodline awakening.

18
00:01:43,572 --> 00:01:51,612
The scar on my left wrist split open with
dark gold. Demonic patterns crawled
through my blood and bones.

19
00:01:52,012 --> 00:01:54,903
Demonic aura detected. Can devour, refine,
and seize its art.

20
00:01:55,603 --> 00:01:58,563
Your eyes... What are you?

21
00:01:58,963 --> 00:02:01,403
Who I am does not matter.

22
00:02:01,803 --> 00:02:07,963
What matters is this: from today on, in
this cold palace, I decide who lives and
who dies.

23
00:02:08,963 --> 00:02:13,363
Madam Liu is a demon. How many more hide
in this man-eating palace?

24
00:02:13,763 --> 00:02:16,803
Only now you know fear? Too late.
